{
 "name": "RPlog_Reenlistment",
 "title": "Reenlistment",
 "summary": "In the Neimoidia Room of Zubindi Hakoon's opulent Silverwood House of Fashion on Caspar, the Presav Crestian and the doctor Lynae Cassius's adopted brother, Captain Sadim Gnik, court her to reenlist in the Caspian service -- as an Admiral. Over Ithorian brandy and warm family banter, they make their case: Caspar lost its way through isolationism and now, allied to the evolving Imperium, needs gifted officers like the former Imperial Commodore. Lynae presses them on what truly distinguishes the reborn Imperium from the Empire she once served, weighing the politics, her son Andrev's legacy, and the shadow of the Sith Malign. Drawn by the prospect of meaningful work and the chance to linger near her son, Lynae accepts the commission, returning Sadim's salute as Admiral Cassius.",
